Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.36,0:15:21.62,*Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}傾いてゆく陽射しが\N西沈的落日餘暉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.03,0:15:28.18,*Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}長い坂道 照らしている\N照在綿長的坡道上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.50,0:15:34.07,*Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}君はひとりで走る\N你獨自一人飛奔著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.03,0:15:41.03,*Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}渇いた喉おさえて\N忍受著乾渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.66,0:15:47.99,*Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}もつれそうになる足元\N腳步漸顯凌亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.30,0:15:54.57,*Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}あきらめがまた襲いかかる\N放棄的念頭再次襲上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.09,0:16:00.84,*Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}予測できないハプニング\N事情的發展出乎意料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.50,0:16:07.16,*Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}軌道はずれた夢\N夢想已然脫軌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.16,0:16:20.80,*Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}心 壊れてく 痛みの中\N即使心已沈浸在崩壞痛苦中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.02,0:16:27.26,*Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}忘れないで欲しい\N卻不願忘卻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.76,0:16:34.35,*Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}ここに居るから\N因為有你在此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.64,0:00:21.44,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找尋著看不見的明天 著急地用手觸摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.60,0:00:25.95,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.10,0:00:38.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來是沒有出口的迷宮 就像需要解謎的拼圖一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.20,0:00:49.84,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有奇跡出現  夢想也將成為勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.05,0:00:54.94,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.11,0:00:57.86,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.01,0:01:00.36,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  因為那份思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:03.65,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我了無形的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.93,0:01:09.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像稍微感受到了迷惘和煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.80,0:01:11.33,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.44,0:01:14.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.49,0:01:23.63,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  對你的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.64,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.68,0:21:50.95,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在心中綻放的玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.10,0:21:57.82,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中燃盡  僅是一束火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.03,0:22:06.46,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滿是隔閡的街上 如遊戲般的迷失自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.59,0:22:10.74,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小丑的心情躊躇著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.58,0:22:19.05,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要踐踏悲傷的殘片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.20,0:22:23.43,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人在未來中戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.01,0:22:31.57,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解開今晚的謎底仍然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.81,0:22:36.06,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up！真面目  Hurry up！回到從前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.35,0:22:43.61,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is passion　兩個人的手中充滿的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.73,0:22:50.57,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入黑暗之中   想緊緊擁抱住陽光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.00,0:22:56.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在迷宮中相互Kiss
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.24,0:23:05.14,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁向樂園  僅差一道門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.13,0:00:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時代的演進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.93,0:00:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困難的案件也與日俱增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.63,0:00:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事件是尋人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.53,0:00:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛的火花是不會熄滅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.63,0:00:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透了人內心真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.53,0:00:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.84,0:00:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.03,0:00:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.03,0:01:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙人掌花殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.73,0:01:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫岡谷典子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.23,0:01:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.43,0:01:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是想調查北川強史這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.84,0:01:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.04,0:01:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 請問一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.04,0:01:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟這個北川是什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.04,0:02:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在六月初的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.35,0:02:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到信州去旅遊的時候認識他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.95,0:02:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.05,0:02:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我對他還沒有什麼感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.16,0:02:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這一陣子 卻有種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.32,0:02:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我覺得非要見到他不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.03,0:02:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.73,0:02:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是愛上了這個姓北川的小伙子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.34,0:02:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是單純尋人的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.24,0:02:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用我出面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.54,0:02:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請喝茶 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.05,0:02:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.75,0:02:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她為什麼這麼緊張啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.05,0:02:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手上有沒有和他有關的東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.75,0:02:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.55,0:02:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有他的車牌號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.23,0:02:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特地畫了張他的肖像畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人長得非常有個性啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.43,0:02:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞭解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事就包在我身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.93,0:02:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張畫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.24,0:02:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.54,0:03:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕鬆的工作又上門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.74,0:03:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了車牌號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.35,0:03:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要到交通局去查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.85,0:03:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就知道他的住址了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.45,0:03:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.55,0:03:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是因為喜歡這個人才要找他的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不管是肖像畫還是隨筆素描
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.53,0:03:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很自然地就會反映出畫圖人的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.13,0:03:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼看那幅肖像畫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少在這裡亂說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.34,0:03:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是有時間在這裡磨蹭的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.64,0:03:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如快點去做功課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.54,0:03:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.74,0:03:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.84,0:03:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後你別對爸爸的工作…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.55,0:03:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡谷小姐的住址是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.65,0:03:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要插手這件事喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.73,0:03:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的資料我都記住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條手帕是她的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.73,0:03:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.44,0:04:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…三百九十八號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.44,0:04:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫羅蘭別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.14,0:04:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.44,0:04:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.55,0:04:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特地跑來送回我的手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.55,0:04:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.55,0:04:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喝可可亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你等一下哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的房間好乾淨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.83,0:04:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.43,0:04:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐是做什麼工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.93,0:04:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.53,0:04:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在一家貿易公司上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.63,0:04:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經辭職了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.04,0:04:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.74,0:04:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我生了一場病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想趁這段時間把身體養好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.24,0:04:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.93,0:04:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏沒有用油的爐子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是對付色狼用的瓦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.16,0:04:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張照片是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的日期是五月九號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.63,0:05:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.83,0:05:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子的房間有這麼好看嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然被你看到讓我難為情的東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.64,0:05:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是前一陣子他竟然把我甩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說我現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會想要找個新的男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.33,0:05:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.03,0:05:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人跟畫像上的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.63,0:05:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在感覺上差好多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.43,0:05:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想換個其他類型的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.13,0:05:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會相處得比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣子而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.13,0:05:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再談我的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.13,0:05:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講一點你的事情來聽聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定有女朋友了對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.03,0:05:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.43,0:05:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我還是沒有套出她的話來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.04,0:05:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆等叔叔回來再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.94,0:05:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.25,0:05:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的住址真的會這麼容易找到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.35,0:06:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有去水族館了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.06,0:06:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.82,0:06:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以摸到海豚的感覺真的好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是天公不作美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.73,0:06:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為今天不下雨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.93,0:06:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔今天還在調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.04,0:06:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫北川的男人搬了家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.34,0:06:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有到交通局那裡去登記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下要多花點時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.75,0:06:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道他的車牌號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特地跑來找偵探幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.63,0:06:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的表情怎麼那麼悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然想起有一件急事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.04,0:06:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.93,0:06:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.85,0:07:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著花還穿著喪服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.65,0:07:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去掃墓嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.14,0:07:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰的墓呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墓碑好像還很新的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.14,0:07:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.54,0:07:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐伯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間過得真快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.75,0:07:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事情已經過了快半年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.75,0:07:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的身體怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.55,0:07:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年前承蒙你的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.26,0:07:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.96,0:07:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是幫助妳恢復而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.73,0:07:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正努力的是妳自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.03,0:07:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.83,0:07:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然碰到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是去喝杯咖啡吧 怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.33,0:07:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.73,0:07:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得馬上趕回去才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.14,0:07:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我開車送妳回去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.84,0:08:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.55,0:08:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.03,0:08:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.75,0:08:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰的墓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.16,0:08:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我一個朋友的墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.12,0:08:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.63,0:08:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原來還以為是剛才回去的那個姐姐的男朋友的墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.53,0:08:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼說也沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不僅是我的好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.43,0:08:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是她的未婚夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.84,0:08:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未婚夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是什麼時候死的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.14,0:08:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年六月初的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.23,0:08:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.34,0:08:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.24,0:08:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是照片上的那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.24,0:08:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是我的男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是前一陣子他竟然把我甩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.55,0:08:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.65,0:08:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典子小姐騙我說她是被他甩掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 那是她死去的未婚夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.93,0:08:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.73,0:08:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是怎麼死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.03,0:08:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是交通事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.73,0:09:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個開車到信州一個叫美之高原的地方兜風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸撞上了山壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 請問一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.04,0:09:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟這個北川是什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.64,0:09:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在六月初
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.75,0:09:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到信州去旅遊的時候認識他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.95,0:09:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說她是在未婚夫出了車禍的時候認識那個人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.23,0:09:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識一個叫北川強史的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.83,0:09:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個開著一輛紅色跑車的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開著紅色的跑車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.53,0:09:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.93,0:09:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快點說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.94,0:09:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事跟那位大姐姐有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.54,0:09:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和典子有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.25,0:09:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到鼎鼎大名的毛利名偵探會找個小孩子來當助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不這麼說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不會把實情告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.73,0:10:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要調查什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.13,0:10:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒辦法把詳情全告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.23,0:10:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我想先知道典子姐姐未婚夫的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫山口達男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.04,0:10:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和典子在同一家公司上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.44,0:10:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才聽到紅色跑車的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐伯叔叔你嚇了一大跳對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.75,0:10:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實在車禍發生之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.85,0:10:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶然聽到她對警方說的一段話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的跑車啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.56,0:10:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.32,0:10:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時車上坐著一對情侶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.43,0:10:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們一直在追著我們的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.33,0:10:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們為了擺脫才會出意外的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.13,0:10:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車禍現場有兩種不同的輪胎痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.23,0:10:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們為什麼要這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.24,0:10:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是故意挑釁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始他們的車跟在我們後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.24,0:10:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停地按改裝過的喇叭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.64,0:10:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就讓他們先走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們又在我們前面蛇行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是那輛車子不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.03,0:10:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.03,0:10:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達男才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.55,0:11:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會派機動搜查隊進行調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.36,0:11:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就算抓到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.63,0:11:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會判很重的刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.43,0:11:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.23,0:11:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說他們的車撞到你們的車 那就不一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.93,0:11:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是照現在的情況來看 這場車禍發生的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.24,0:11:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是由於山口先生的疏忽所致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.64,0:11:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.64,0:11:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.24,0:11:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛車的樣子以及車牌號碼妳還記得嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.95,0:11:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡谷小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.45,0:11:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那個時候很肯定地告訴警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經全部都不記得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.53,0:11:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.53,0:11:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典子小姐是這麼說的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.23,0:11:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我看她心事重重的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.73,0:11:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還說她不記得那對情侶的樣子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後 因為沒有線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.34,0:11:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方的調查行動在持續了一個月之後就停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.53,0:11:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她提到的那個線索是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.55,0:12:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 我有他的車牌號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.65,0:12:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特地畫了張他的肖像畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.65,0:12:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人長得非常有個性啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.35,0:12:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實典子記得很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.85,0:12:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的車牌號碼和他的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.83,0:12:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她卻沒有把這些告訴警方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.03,0:12:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想親自報仇嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.23,0:12:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐伯叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.33,0:12:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你跟典子姐姐談到復健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.63,0:12:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一個醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.44,0:12:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個意外之後她的復健一直是由我來負責的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.34,0:12:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時典子的情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.44,0:12:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的很努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.04,0:12:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人可能要大半年才能康復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她卻只花了3個月就出院了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也嚇了一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.22,0:12:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她要對那對情侶報仇的決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才使她迅速站起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.33,0:12:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐伯叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.43,0:12:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在立刻到典子姐姐那裡去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.33,0:13:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.43,0:13:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.93,0:13:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在叔叔找到那個北川之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.54,0:13:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要讓典子小姐改變心意才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.64,0:13:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要怎麼做才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.84,0:13:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.45,0:13:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.15,0:13:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是蝦蛄仙人掌的刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.72,0:13:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一陣子我到朋友家搬了一盆回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定是那個時候沾上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.62,0:13:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝦蛄仙人掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個該不會是山口先生的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的年紀雖然很輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是對養仙人掌卻有濃厚的興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.63,0:13:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車禍發生之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.03,0:13:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典子把那些仙人掌當成是他的遺物全給我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.14,0:13:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搬了一盆是因為有人想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.84,0:13:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我想典子是害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.54,0:13:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起山口先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.81,0:13:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才決定暫時先放到我那裡來保管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.02,0:13:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.12,0:13:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種蝦蛄仙人掌別名叫做聖誕仙人掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.92,0:13:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐伯叔叔你家遠不遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.53,0:14:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.53,0:14:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就住在到典子家的這條路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.23,0:14:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼先去你家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.13,0:14:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來典子好像還沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不知道叔叔什麼時候會打電話給她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.74,0:14:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該盡可能待在家裡才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.35,0:14:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男的住址已經查到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 毛利偵探事務所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 你已經到家了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.02,0:14:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不是那個叫北川的人的住址已經查到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.02,0:14:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 已經查到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.33,0:14:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了我不少時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.73,0:14:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我的鞋底還磨掉了3公分呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.63,0:14:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊 柯南嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.33,0:14:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我已經把地址告訴過她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.04,0:14:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.14,0:14:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個男的現在已經和另一個女的同居了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.04,0:14:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的戀情才開始 真讓人太遺憾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.24,0:14:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把他的住址告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.14,0:14:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛要告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.15,0:14:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快點的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.35,0:14:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人很有可能會被她殺掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.72,0:16:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.23,0:16:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典子小姐很有可能先到交通局那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.73,0:16:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查過北川強史這個人的住址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.54,0:17:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為不知道他搬家後的新地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.54,0:17:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會拜託叔叔調查的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.54,0:17:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就她康復速度這麼快這一點來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.24,0:17:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓她改變向北川報仇的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.65,0:17:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是不太可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.42,0:17:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會用什麼方法來報仇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.32,0:17:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山口先生是當場死亡的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.42,0:17:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說他們在撞到山壁的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.43,0:17:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.43,0:17:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真正的死因是被火燒死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.13,0:17:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.53,0:17:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他被救出車子之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.03,0:17:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子的汽油就已經先引爆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.04,0:17:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她房裡的那桶根本不是什麼燈油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.94,0:17:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.04,0:17:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.82,0:18:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳不是那個時候的那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.42,0:18:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子你還記得我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.22,0:18:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想要幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次的事故又不是我們的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.43,0:18:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是來聽你們狡辯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓你們兩個納命來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.23,0:18:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.44,0:18:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個人渣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.44,0:18:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.44,0:18:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓你們嘗嘗死亡的痛苦滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.25,0:18:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看是妳的腦筋短路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.52,0:19:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在屋頂上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.73,0:19:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在能夠讓她放棄報復念頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.23,0:19:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有這個方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想要幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.92,0:19:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.52,0:19:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典子 妳千萬別做傻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不要過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.03,0:19:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你把他們殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.53,0:19:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山口先生也不可能起死回生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.13,0:19:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.33,0:19:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我現在沒有別的辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.13,0:19:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.24,0:19:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳如果把火點燃的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.54,0:19:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳自己也會被燒著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.14,0:19:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.44,0:19:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有達男的將來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.34,0:19:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說已經沒有任何意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.25,0:19:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我死之前只想把這兩個人殺掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.93,0:20:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.83,0:20:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.93,0:20:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種蝦蛄仙人掌的花好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.54,0:20:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在國外 因為它只在冬天開花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.84,0:20:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以經常被當作聖誕禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.44,0:20:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是因為這樣也被稱作聖誕仙人掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.32,0:20:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝦蛄仙人掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是達男養的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.33,0:20:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.32,0:20:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他養的這些仙人掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.93,0:20:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我當成是他的遺物帶回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.85,0:21:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.45,0:21:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山口雖然已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要仙人掌還在開花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.52,0:21:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就還活在這個世界上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.14,0:21:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.14,0:23:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天你要是一起來就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.35,0:23:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水族館好好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.61,0:23:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們三個還一起餵東西給海豚吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.42,0:23:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過元太在那裡還滑了一跤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.82,0:23:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作人員正好把那個瞬間拍下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.43,0:23:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.73,0:23:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的...好好玩的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.34,0:23:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好我沒有一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.14,0:23:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙給他買了巨額保險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.52,0:23:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有五億元呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.62,0:24:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且為那個傢伙的不在場證明作證的人就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.02,0:24:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.13,0:24:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.33,0:24:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把那個腐爛的靈魂糾正過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.33,0:24:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.73,0:24:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅鬼村火祭殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.04,0:24:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.34,0:24:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左撇子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.83,0:24:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回事件有點難度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.33,0:24:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把原作讀過了喔
